QuestData.Title: Serpents from the Deep
QuestData.Description: Hail, $c.$B$BMy village of Jandvik has fallen under siege by a group of naga called the Sashj'tar.$B$BNormally I would not seek out the help of an outsider, but we are facing an enemy that we are incapable of defeating.$B$BMany powerful elven relics can be found in the ruins around Jandvik. In exchange for your help, you will have your just rewards.$B$BDo we have an accord?
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Toryl outside of Jandvik.
